  <!-- EN: The site has been found and raided by others. The quest [resolvedQuestName] has expired. -->
  <VFEV_OpportunitySite_LegendaryGrave.LetterTextQuestExpired.slateRef>Это место было разграблено кем-то другим. Время, отведённое для задания [resolvedQuestName], истекло.</VFEV_OpportunitySite_LegendaryGrave.LetterTextQuestExpired.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Quest failed: [resolvedQuestName] -->
  <VFEV_OpportunitySite_LegendaryGrave.LetterLabelQuestFailed.slateRef>Задание провалено: «[resolvedQuestName]»</VFEV_OpportunitySite_LegendaryGrave.LetterLabelQuestFailed.slateRef>
